WEBVTT

00:01:59.495 --> 00:02:01.950
You've probably been told
the same thing at work:

00:02:01.974 --> 00:02:04.061
you have to fix your weaknesses.

00:02:04.695 --> 00:02:07.941
But it's a mistake to just focus
on what's weakest.

00:02:08.252 --> 00:02:09.418
Great things can happen

00:02:09.442 --> 00:02:11.799
if you have the chance
to build on your strengths.

00:02:11.823 --> 00:02:16.688
(Theme music)

00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:20.720
I'm Adam Grant, and this is WorkLife,
my podcast with TED.

00:02:20.744 --> 00:02:22.490
I'm an organizational psychologist.

00:02:22.797 --> 00:02:25.396
I study how to make work not suck.

00:02:25.982 --> 00:02:27.133
In this show,

00:02:27.157 --> 00:02:30.256
I'm inviting myself inside the minds
of some truly unusual people,